{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But very soon, we found out that this type of organization doesn't have a future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just friendship doesn't have a future.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to be attached to some kind of compassion, some charity, to something that would do-- that you would do for others, rather than for yourself.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because this is a self-serving-- would be self-- too much self-serving to really be able to be sustained.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we have-- in this organization, we have organized all kinds of committees in charge of charities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You established a welfare fund, which is helping Jews that still live today in Krakow and Jews of Krakow descent that live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this welfare fund exists already now for over 27 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we are sending money to a lot of Jews in Krakow and in Israel every month.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many people are in this organization?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The organization now has a little less than 400 family members.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But besides that, we attached ourselves to the causes of Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are supporting many causes, like Israel bonds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have a function every year and we try to sell Israel bonds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some years, we are selling bonds for over $1 million, by our organization alone, without the help of outsiders.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we also adopted organizations in Israel, like Akim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Akim is an organization for the rehabilitation of handicapped children in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in 1975, this was a completely new organization, Akim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got wind of it, and particularly our women got very enthusiastic about the idea of helping handicapped children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we formed a special committee that would raise funds to help Akim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now we have an establishment in Hadera [DRINKS] that was built by our funds, and we keep supporting it ever since.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
